{"tid":2447723,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"全民造星陰濕公廁賤閪 關嘉敏 卡文 @ Bingo 追擊區","createTime":"2021-03-15T11:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T13:34:03.000Z","uid":132986,"like":108,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"04218237874acf975b0fd80b649d0f37f966607f","tid":2447723,"uid":132986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:41:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>造星陰濕公廁賤閪關嘉敏追擊區</strong></span></span><br />\n<blockquote>追返上個po 睇到個公廁閪文點樣乞陳伯比佢一齊live<br />\n屌佢老母真係乞衣黎<br />\n<br />\n諗起佢話佢要做solo歌手<br />\n我全家都 吓 出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咬字又唔撚清<br />\n好似含住撚讀歌詞咁<br />\n<br />\n繼續去食仔算啦<br />\n校服任砌千人斬 天堂鳥 班長 cy 狗公dancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">死lur request入陳柏宇ig live</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>陳伯開緊live 老婆喺隔離 之後假閪文啲fans 係咁話佢想join 陳伯就婉拒咗話唔好啦會怕羞 跟住佢本人入埋嚟 叫陳伯快啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 迫完人畀佢一齊開live 仲迫人讚佢 最後假閪文講多謝你呀 好開心 哈哈 假撚到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bm9JyGn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbm9JyGn.png&h=c4e67289&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>佢乞左兩三次入live<br />\n然後再乞鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三條火車軌不得了<br />\n快d搵d精去敷下塊面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩抖音微博都上唔到位<br />\n死lur入陳伯live ig 2萬幾升到5萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係佢叫陳伯快d叫佢比佢入live就知佢咩人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拒絕兩三次都咁撚厚臉皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqJBTGw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqJBTGw.png&h=90a3fd90&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">五音不全想做solo歌手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>兩個都係臭閪<br />\n但你講蠢就一定係odiu<br />\n所謂精人出口笨人出手<br />\nOdiu當眾屌前隊友<br />\n公廁文陰d陰d係報導講<br />\n<br />\nCarman識搵鏡頭扮喊搶fo<br />\n識食班長cy打好關係<br />\n識扮內斂扮柔弱<br />\n但觀眾唔係傻架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旗都扯唔撚起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見fb yt d人話佢靚<br />\n搏頭橫撚到摔角咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要樣冇樣<br />\n要身材冇身材<br />\n要歌藝冇歌藝<br />\n<br />\n公廁關嘉敏你唔好咁有自信做到solo歌手啦<br />\n有冇諗過你把老牛聲好閪難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n著返校服比人屌算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"022a9822dc201afcaff008d79308eab09337c903","tid":2447723,"uid":132986,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">pre round已經搵鏡頭扮喊搶fo</span></span><br />\n<br />\n孔仙洲性器仆街好多<br />\n陰濕到仆街<br />\n投完FAKER 然後佢走果陣扮咸推FAKER 走搶鏡頭<br />\n陳伯開IG LIVE人地老婆係隔離都要格硬REQUEST<br />\n仲未計689 晉十果陣佢個閪面樣[/quote]<br />\n臭閪敏太over啦<br />\n投完faker話唔可以輸呀<br />\n輸左會好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比臭閪敏 odiu 班長（已食）三個夾埋投走左<br />\n同呢三件垃圾同隊就真係慘喇<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">不過好撚開心十強冇你份呀公廁關嘉敏</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊忽靚呀？求其cap圖都cap到佢個閪樣<br />\n話佢似娜姐簡直侮辱左娜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMBG4Qc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMBG4Qc.jpg&h=ee39d9ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">男既食曬  女既陰走</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>[quote]佢呢種死臭閪好撚識扮<br />\n鏡頭前無遺憾遇上強敵<br />\n又係背後陰d陰d做小動作<br />\n就好似陰d陰d係報導屌鳩前隊友<br />\n唔同odiu個種當面屌<br />\n其實關嘉敏都係臭閪<br />\n係陰濕型臭閪<br />\n睇既男人唔受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我由頭追擊到尾<br />\n關嘉敏一出場已經覺得佢係好撚扮野個d臭閪<br />\n可能食到個d會受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班長 cy 狗公dancer個d<br />\n<br />\n唔使問法官大人<br />\n有得屌我都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o3dinB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo3dinB2.png&h=b0b6b270&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bd07a84dd139512f6cd79d1f35e79181033d83b8","tid":2447723,"uid":132986,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:44:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">當個個參賽者都避嫌del po del wb<br />\n關嘉敏呢隻臭雞仲用緊wb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n又抖音又微博<br />\n躝返去同天堂鳥含撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3ieFpk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3ieFpk.jpg&h=365bf4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzNrwv1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzNrwv1.png&h=e0cf7b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見d人讚佢應該入10強<br />\n話佢唱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（咪玩啦 想mute撚左成首歌）<br />\n跳得又麻麻（其實有d跳快左）<br />\n讚佢靚所以更加應該入10強<br />\n呢個咩原因黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔係選美<br />\n再者佢邊撚度靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去蘭桂坊都大撚把佢呢種公廁樣<br />\n仲要裝假狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得膊頭橫係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ySvdKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ySvdKu.png&h=b0c42640&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]<br />\n邊個再話佢靚既<br />\n將佢d相曬海報貼床頭唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"dfd7adc2b6a95d2f8ae6993125116cff70695116","tid":2447723,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"???????"},{"pid":"a1ea8b97380673527488460f0b25b8b993206cb3","tid":2447723,"uid":132986,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">CY比公廁賤閪關嘉敏趙完鬆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇長追每個post唔知有冇人講過<br />\n前幾日睇番CY ig save低既live發現原來佢有講番dance battle幽襪個幕係因為個卡文跌低左 CY扶番卡文起身 跟住比卡文踩甩左隻鞋跟 佢先要著番隻鞋 <br />\n希望多啲人知佢當時唔係為左幽隻襪而係為著番好隻鞋 雖然佢跳舞真係唔叻好多step都跟得唔足 但係睇番佢當時並唔係對個show唔上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>個時都有人講 佢係甩咗鞋<br />\n但無咩人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲人覺得佢個時係組內老鼠屎</blockquote>我都係睇佢live 突然有觀眾問起佢幽襪個幕 先知原來係比人踩甩<br />\n佢係個live都有講 終於有人問起佢呢個問題 話之前一直冇機會解釋番 因為當時鏡頭好遠影唔到整個過程 <br />\n不過我再睇番段片真係見到少少片段影到卡文係地下企起身跟住CY又掂住佢 應該就係個陣扶番起卡文再幽隻鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過因為咁樣 覺得佢個性格都好好唔會為左自己而篤人灰 對佢好感大增左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過卡文當時又唔解釋番令我對佢更加討厭 假面人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qdyY64Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqdyY64Y.jpg&h=0add85ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n造星公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"